name: launcher_test_app_prod
docker_compose_file:
version: '3.8'

services:
  launcher:
    image: nearone/mpc-tee-launcher:2a6c73ad7d64604560498547c45a8919a1e4122c-2a6c73a
    

 # isuse #531: TODO (security): Replace with a specific image digest
    container_name: launcher

    environment:
      - DOCKER_CONTENT_TRUST=1
      - DEFAULT_IMAGE_DIGEST=sha256:f4bea6e5bd4b652455daa25916d6d99ea6b1b8905059cb606f6eea494e83d063

    volumes:
      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock
      - /var/run/dstack.sock:/var/run/dstack.sock
      - /tapp:/tapp:ro
      - shared-volume:/mnt/shared:ro

    security_opt:
      - no-new-privileges:true

    read_only: true

    tmpfs:
      - /tmp

volumes:
  shared-volume:
    name: shared-volume
